# Google reCAPTCHA v2 Configuration
# Get your keys from: https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin
# 1. Go to https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin
# 2. Register a new site with reCAPTCHA v2 (Checkbox)
# 3. Add your domain (or localhost for development)
# 4. Copy the Site Key and Secret Key below

# Client-side key (used in the frontend)
VITE_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your_site_key_here

# Server-side secret (used in the backend API)
RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here
